# View Renderer Rules (Spec -> UI)

Views must render from `phaseX.views.json` and `final_dashboard.views.json`.

## Chart Library
- Use Recharts as default.
- Do not introduce Chart.js.

## Supported View Types (must exist as components)
- `ui_hero_card`, `ui_detail_card`, `ui_cards`, `ui_canvas_card`
- `ui_grid_2x2`, `ui_channel_stack`, `ui_kanban_light`, `ui_board_4_columns`, `ui_list_with_actions`
- `ui_hex_prism` (Brand Identity Prism)
- `ui_brand_wheel` (Markensteuerrad)
- `recharts_radar`, `recharts_bar`, `recharts_scatter`

## Styling
- Bold/high-contrast, card-first.
- Use shadcn/ui components whenever possible.
- Avoid large paragraphs; prefer structured fields.
